channel.description:
Jesus answered, "I am the way and the truth and the life. No one comes to the Father except through me." (John 14:6)

For God so loved the world that He gave His one and only Son, that whoever believes in Him shall not perish but have eternal life. (John 3:16)

Jesus is THE ONLY WAY to go to heaven! 

Repent your sins and believe in Jesus as your Savior to go to heaven. 

We can not go to heaven by our rightness because we are all sinners. We could remove these sins only by blood of Jesus who died for our sins.

Whenever we repent our sins, God forgive us. So surrender to Jesus. He could save us. Jesus is the only way. 

There is no other name! ONLY JESUS!!!

So believers could go to heaven by the grace of God. Kingdom of heaven is our eternal home. 

I hope all believers have great rewards in heaven and have love in Jesus deeply.
channel.title: HisKingdomForever
